      "id": "c_text_1",
      "type": "text",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "props": {
        "content": "## Our Story\n\nFounded in 2014 by coffee enthusiasts Sarah and Mike, Artisan Coffee began as a dream to bring exceptional coffee to our local community. What started as a small corner shop has grown into a beloved gathering place where neighbors become friends over perfectly crafted cups of coffee.\n\nWe believe that great coffee brings people together, and every cup we serve is made with care, attention to detail, and a commitment to quality that you can taste.",
        "format": "markdown",
        "alignment": "left",
        "size": "md"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c_card_1",
      "type": "card",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "props": {
        "title": "Visit Our Shop",
        "description": "Experience the Artisan Coffee atmosphere in person",
        "content": "**Hours:**\nMonday - Friday: 6:00 AM - 8:00 PM\nSaturday - Sunday: 7:00 AM - 9:00 PM\n\n**Location:**\n123 Main Street\nDowntown District\n\n**Phone:** (555) 123-BREW",
        "style": "glass",
        "padding": "lg",
        "hover": true
      }
    },
